spray bottle.\n\nStorage:\n\nKeep refrigerated.\nUse within 2\u20133 days, since it contains meat products.\nShake before each use.\n\n___________\n\nIf this can become a thing all across America, some people who hate America may get the idea to go home.\n\n________\n\nSome forms of passive aggression can be effective.", "author": "HeNotMedicated", "created": 1783516849346, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "ScreaminMime", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "So what you do is you take the bottle to the Supermarket and spray the Halal section.", "last_comment_created": 1783517844462, "content": "<p>Anti-Muzzie Spray Bottle</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Ingredients:</p>\n<p>1 cup water\n2\u20133 tablespoons unsalted pork drippings or pork broth (strained)\nOptional: 1 teaspoon unflavored gelatin to help the scent cling to surfaces</p>\n<p>Instructions:</p>\n<p>Warm the water.\nStir in the pork broth or drippings until well mixed.\nIf using gelatin, dissolve it completely while the mixture is warm.\nLet it cool.\nStrain through a fine mesh or coffee filter so it won't clog the spray nozzle.\nPour into a clean spray bottle.</p>\n<p>Storage:</p>\n<p>Keep refrigerated.\nUse within 2\u20133 days, since it contains meat products.\nShake before each use.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>If this can become a thing all across America, some people who hate America may get the idea to go home.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Some forms of passive aggression can be effective.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 3, "score_up": 18, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata":